INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('141', '1', '2012-07-18 15:58:12', '2012-07-18 13:58:12', 'In the last week of July, SPBH will run a programme of workshops and classes at this years’ TVFL Summer School.  Nestled within the surrounding territory of Luciana, the fourteenth-century Luciano Palace will play host to the group.  Under the guidance of SPBH Founder, Bruno Ceschel, participants will be immersed in a series of exercises that will act as catalysts for emotional exploration and response, and offer the opportunity of a fresh start to produce original photographic works. Tools and skills will be made available during the workshop so as to shape a photographic book and to understand what the possibilities of production, distribution and marketing are. The analysis of several publishing models from the most significant works of contemporary artists and photographers will be integral to the discourse, and discussion will focus on editing, sequencing and design, from both a theoretical and a practical standpoint.\n\nInfo: http://www.theviewfromlucania.com/?p=1019&lang=en', 'SELF PUBLISH, BE HAPPY SUMMER CAMP - Lucania, Italy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'self-publish-be-happy-summer-camp-lucania-italy', '', '', '2012-07-23 13:27:36', '2012-07-23 11:27:36', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=141', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('142', '1', '2012-07-18 15:58:12', '2012-07-18 13:58:12', 'Domingo 22 Julio / Sunday 22nd July 2012\n\nTHE SUNDAY JOINT FIESTA EN LA PLAYA #2 @ LASAL\n\nWILL SUMSUCH + DJ ROGER C + JOSH WEITZER (percusión)\n\nLasal Xiringuito\nPlaya de Cavaio\nArenys de Mar\nCatalunya\n\nwww.lasal.com\n\n16:30-22:00\nEntrada Gratis\n\nMusica: Funk, Hip-Hop, Soul, Jazz, Latin, Afrobeat, Reggae, Brazilian y mucho mas.\n\nGetting There / Cómo Llegar\n----------------------\nTREN RODALIES (R1) / LOCAL TRAIN (R1)\nBarcelona, Placa Catalunya (Rodalies Estacion) - Arenys de Mar\nSalida Placa Catalunya: a las 17 y 47 minutos después de la hora (53 minutos)\nDeparts Placa Catalunya: 17 and 48 minutes past the hour (53 minutes)\nUltima Tren / Last Train: Arenys de Mar - Barcelona 22.10\nMas Informacion: http://www.renfe.com/EN/viajeros/cercanias/barcelona/index.html\n\nREUNIÓN DE TIEMPO Y LUGAR / MEETING TIME & PLACE \n14:45 fuera CAFE ZURICH, abajo FNAC, Placa Catalunya por tren 15:17 \n14:45 outside CAFE ZURICH, below FNAC, Placa Catalunya for train at 15:17\n\nCaminar - Playa de Cavaio 10 minutos\nWalking - Playa de Cavaio 10 minutes\n\nCoche / Car: Carretera N-11 Arenys de Mar\nMapa: www.lasal.com\nGoogle Map: http://bit.ly/jkIrJl\n\n////////////////////////////////\n\nWILL SUMSUCH (Brighton, UK)\n\nBiographia en Inglis\n\nWill Sumsuch has been a musician, producer and DJ for over a decade, gathering both a grass roots fan-base and industry respect, due to his unique ear for quality music and distinctive production style. His tracks have been used on national TV adverts in the UK, played on radio worldwide and released on countless compilation albums.\n\nHis first two releases on Urban Torque recordings received support from luminaries including Ben Watt, Justin Martin, Jody Wisternoff & Ricky Ryan. Will\'s remixes have been released on Hed Kandi and Time Records among others, and he has recently been signed by Scope for his brand new label, Seven Music.\n\nSumsuch began hosting the Etoka Records show on Ibiza Global in 2009, and still finds time to present a show every month, showcasing the finest underground deep house. In the past year he\'s played at numerous venues across Europe, including Pacha and The Egg in London, as well as Ahjo in Helsinki.\n\nUpcoming projects include \'Lifers\', a collaboration with tech house don Harold Heath, a new solo release on Etoka Records, and eventually a solo album, where you can expect to hear Sumsuch return to his downtempo roots.\n\nwww.facebook.com/will.sumsuch\n\n////////////////////////////////\n\nDJ ROGER C\n\npromotor y residente Dj - The Sunday Joint, The Joint Sessions, Hot Sauce\n\nwww.facebook.com/djrogerc\n\n////////////////////////////////\n\nJOSH WEITZER - Percusión\n\n////////////////////////////////\n\n\nLASAL XIRINGUITO\n\nLasal ofrece, siete días a la semana, de mayo a septiembre, un amplio abanico de posibilidades a todo aquel que se acerque, desde el primer café hasta la última copa, pasando por el aperitivo a la sombra de mediodía, comerse un bocadillo o una ensalada, o ver como se esconde el sol con el mar como testigo. Los sonidos y los ritmos de lasal ambientan la playa desde las primeras horas de la mañana hasta la madrugada, en un marco fresco y relajado.', 'Sunday Joint Fiesta en la Playa #2 @ Lasal Xiringuito con Will Sumsuch, Roger C & Josh Weitzer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-sunday-joint-fiesta-en-la-playa-2-lasal-xiringuito', '', '', '2012-07-20 13:27:39', '2012-07-20 11:27:39', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=142', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
