INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('836', '0', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', 'METROPOLITAN GARDEN\nby Amnesia Milano\n\nSabato 18 Agosto 2012 - ore 23.00\nPunta dell’Est, circonvallazione Idroscalo Est 21, INGRESSO B - Segrate MI\n\nMain Room:\n\nMATTEO VANTI aka MATTHE (Memento Label - IT)\n\nIVAN N. aka PHREEK PLUS ONE (Compost Black, Amnesia Mi -IT)\n\n\nL\'estate si fa sempre più calda e Metropolitan Garden ti terrà compagnia per tutto Agosto!\n\nOgni sabato sera saremo sulla nuova super terrazza dell’Idroscalo avvolti dai beat più incisivi in circolazione, con proposte artistiche fresche e miti della scena dance contemporanea. Un altro mese fatto di serate indimenticabili, vissute all’aperto nel grande parco fuori città, con il dance floor come protagonista indiscusso delle nostre notti estive. \n\nPrezzi:\n\nINGRESSO UOMO/DONNA 10€ IN LSTA FINO ALLA 1.00\n\nIntero 15€\n\nTavoli:\nPrivè Consolle 150€ x 6 persone con 1 bottiglia\nPista/Terrazza 120€ x 6 persone con 1 bottiglia\n\n• Info line: + 39 347 7591456\nwww.amnesiamilano.com ', 'Metropolitan Garden. Dj\'s: Matteo Vanti, Ivan N aka Phreek Plus One, F. Di Norcia. INGRESSO 10 EURO PER TUTTI.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'metropolitan-garden-djs-matteo-vanti-ivan-n-aka-phreek-plus-one-f-di-norcia-ingresso-10-euro-per-tutti', '', '', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress_old_css/?p=836', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('837', '0', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', 'On Saturday 18th August Tastebudz.inc Deep into Soul move to their new Home Club Nomad for Mr Tastebudz birthday celebrations with \nspecial Guest Groove Assassin.\n\nNick  Moss  aka Groove Assassin has been in the game for 20 years as a DJ and 15 as a producer.Hailing from Sheffield the North of England , Nick was raised on a diet of Funk , Jazz Funk , Latin ,\nSoul and Disco – All elements that he utilizes both in his productions and his Dj sets.\n\nOne of the UK &amp; Europe’s  most respected house music  Dj’s and Producers  , Nick’s original productions and remix work have appeared on such stellar imprints as , DEFECTED RECORDS , MN2S RECORDS ,\nHED KANDI , STEREO SUSHI , MINISTRY OF SOUND , SOUL HEAVEN , JELLYBEAN , KING ST &amp; NITEGROOVES amongst many other legendary house music imprints.\n\nAs a Dj , Nick’s as intuitive as one might expect of a veteran who has watched the house scene go through so many different incarnations. His style ranges from deep underground NY Garage to throbbing deep underground house to main room house music to straight up disco and funk classics , rare groove and soul  – which is to say he truly revels in the diversity of this thing we call house music.\n\nAlongside Nick downstairs keeping things Soulful will be Booker T, Deep into Soul resident Ziggy Funk and Taliwa performing their No 1 smash What you afraid of plus 1 other track, whilst Upstairs taking things a little deeper will be Sy Sez and Crookid.\n\nSo come and join one of London\'s most talked about parties as we begin a new chapter in true Tastebudz style, bringing you two floors of nothing but the very best in House Music and a crowd who love to party.\n\nFull DJ line up\n\nGroove Assassin (Defected Records/MN2S/King Street/Soul Heaven)\n\nBooker T (Kings of Soul)\n\nZiggy Funk (Tastebudz.Inc)\n\nSy Sez (Aphrodisiax/Soul Heaven/Beat Players)\n\nCrookid (Tastebudz.Inc)\n\nTaliwa (Quantize Records/Foliage Records)\n\nEntry on the night £12 or email full names to events@deepintosoul.com for £8 Concessions.\n\nFor all things deep into Soul\n\nwww.deepintosoul.com\n\nTwitter@tastebudzevents\n\nFB group page Deep into Soul\n', 'Tastebudz.inc Deep into Soul Presents Groove Assassin@Scott Tastebudz birthday celebration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tastebudz-inc-deep-into-soul-presents-groove-assassinscott-tastebudz-birthday-celebration', '', '', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress_old_css/?p=837', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('838', '0', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', 'SOUNDS OF SOUL ......... PRESENTS \n\nSounds Of : PETER OAKDEN {Restless Soul} | CARINA RAMOS {Ladies On Rotation} | JAMIE BUCHANAN {78 Edits) \n\nSATURDAY 18TH AUGUST 2012 @ HANOVER 99 \n\n**THIS IS ONE NIGHT YOU ALL DON\'T WANT TO MISS **\n\nI have to admit this is one night we ( SOUNDS OF SOUL) are so looking forward to , Its a shout out to all music lovers - DISCO HEADS | FUNK| SOULFUL HOUSE | SOUL|HIP HOP &amp; all that ....\nWe hope you can all come along to this event - LETS FEEL THE BREEZE FROM THE TUNES !!\n\nA combination of DJ\'s that have one thing in common - MUSIC , with a wealth of producing , collecting , DJin , Sharing  &gt; MUSIC \n\nPETER OAKDEN : Peter is seen as the UK\'s rising talent on the underground scene. The hungry young DJ, producer &amp; label owner released his first solo project for Phil Asher\'s restless soul Music which was supported by Soul Clap, The Revenge, Ugly Drums, Gerd, Glenn Underground plus others. He launched his independent imprint Soul Free Records in 2010 which features underground artists from around the globe. He has future releases already planned for 2012/13 on restless soul, Development Music, Local Talk, Deeper Shades Of House &amp; soulfulbeats. Projects under The True Rebels &amp; Black Sauce guises are continuous along with exciting side project\'s with Lay-Far. http://soundcloud.com/peteroakden\n\nCARINA RAMOS :Carina tends to be seen as the disco spinner but she\'s always throwing in a whole lot of boogie, funk and house too. She started playing a few years back in bars around town, with gigs also at Ultragroove,Ladies On Rotation, Beatbox, Foundation Nation and more recently with Isodisco in Belfast and Six Million Steps at East Village. She\'s warmed up for Marcia Carr, John Morales, Sleazybeats, Sean McCabe and played back room for a whole lot more. You can listen to some of her mixes on her soundcloud page http://soundcloud.com/carinaramos/\n\nJAMIE BUCHANAN :\'Although you may not have heard of him (yet) Edinburgh based DJ/Producer Jamie Buchanan (78Edits) has been making some serious waves on the re-edit, deep/disco scene over the past year and a half. With vinyl releases on labels such as Kolour ltd, Ubiquity, Giant Cuts, Get Down Edits and DJ gigs from Edinburgh to Istanbul this year his very special brand of house tinged disco and soul is not to be missed\' .  http://soundcloud.com/search?q[fulltext]=78+edits\n\n\nDate : Saturday 18th August 2012\n\nVenue : Hanover 99 ( Edinburgh )\n\nTime : 9pm ( Late License Edinburgh Fringe Festival )\n\nDoor : Free \n\nContact : https://www.facebook.com/SOUNDSOFSOULUK\n              :https://www.facebook.com/papajgun\n', 'PETER OAKDEN | CARINA RAMOS |JAMIE BUCHANAN @ Sounds Of Soul', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'peter-oakden-carina-ramos-jamie-buchanan-sounds-of-soul', '', '', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress_old_css/?p=838', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('839', '0', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', 'Para disfrutar de la poesíay hacer que septiembre no se nos haga tan duro volvemos a llevar Poetry Slam a la terraza. Será en el C3Bar en el Centre de Cultura Contemporània de Barcelona (CCCB). Un lugar perfecto para disfrutar de un atardecer de verano lleno de poesía .\nEl Poetry Slam es un campeonato poético donde cada participante tiene 3 minutos para recitar su texto, tras lo cual el público le puntúa eligiendo un ganador. 50 % interpretación, 50 % poesía, así se plantea este torneo poético que ya es todo un referente en la agenda cultural barcelonesa.\nParticiparán los cuatro finalistas de la edición anterior más los ocho primeros en enviar un mail con dos poemas a partir del 27 de agosto a comunicacion@hipnotikfaktory.com\n\nAquí podeís consultar el reglamento del campeonato http://on.fb.me/L6I0u8\n\nOs esperamos', 'Poetry Slam a la fresca - setembre 2012', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'poetry-slam-a-la-fresca-setembre-2012', '', '', '2012-08-18 21:02:48', '2012-08-18 19:02:48', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress_old_css/?p=839', '0', 'ai1ec_event', '', '0');
